		<hr size="1">I asked this on the EQVault board, but it's dead over there.</P><P>Since they're now allowing us to move Blue server characters to the original Zeks, I've been thinking of moving my 28 Dwarf Rogue to Rallos. I have a couple of characters on Sullon Zek, and I like PvP, but I'm wondering what I'll find if I come here. And of course, yes, I'll be naked, so that might make it interesting. </P><P>Just curious if anyone has any thoughts - I'm assuming a much different PKing culture than on Sullon . . . </P><P>I'm also curious about the market and Bazaar here.  Are prices cheaper, more expensive, 'bout the same?</P><P>Message edited by: Kharlisht (9/11/2002 10:26:56 AM)<BR>Edit: Need a better picture.</P><P>Message edited by: Kharlisht (9/11/2002 10:27:54 AM)<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
